  "name": "Ossia",
  "title": "Bewitching Devil",
  "description": "Due to the size of the gap between her physical and mental age, or maybe due to the enormous power dwelling in her body, her mind is trying to catch up abnormally fast. But there is a price for defying the natural order, that is how this world works. And the price for her rapid growth—or rather evolution—was ethics and morals.\n\"Will you play with me...? No, I will make you my playmate myself, hahaha...\"\nWhat makes people unable to look away is that hint of childishness mixed with all the seductiveness, that bit of charm among all the innocence. It shows in her looks, her words, and seems to monopolize the thoughts of those who meet her.",
